{"tid":761764,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Display無乜水冷散熱","createTime":"2018-07-30T16:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T17:13:35.000Z","uid":195438,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a47c8f84cfa487fa6a05ee5ebb880e31806fa7a2","tid":761764,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"CPU唔超頻有幾可會高温，平時打機得嗰60幾度<br />\n但係Display郁啲就70度，夏天80度真係家常便飯<br />\n然後三個風扇就會開晒Turbo咁轉<br />\n<br />\n再加上大部份機箱設計都係不利於Display散熱，下置式火牛<br />\nATX箱仲好啲，但M-ATX已經無乜空間走熱<br />\n<br />\n如果用側透機箱嘅人應該都試過摸塊玻璃<br />\nCPU個位只係暖暖地，Display個位直情係辣手"},{"pid":"493abc4cc2f1929f2c629b709d0cfeca13f5b775","tid":761764,"uid":173741,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:24:52.000Z","msg":"你又講得幾啱喎<br />\n打機既話 張卡永遠都係使用率去到100%<br />\ncpu好少會上到咁高"},{"pid":"0c9ca3d37ad8fc65021bf06f03b44d2848049b67","tid":761764,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"貴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反正80度無乜問題"},{"pid":"4126b319851204186f9610b33294ede6590e385b","tid":761764,"uid":30937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:36:02.000Z","msg":"裝個nzxt水冷顯示卡支架上一體水"},{"pid":"14e04c50e9448b2aff72e8500d0f7b65a47503c9","tid":761764,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:49:44.000Z","msg":"單排又一體水不如風冷，雙排機箱兼容性又低，出黎有幾多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚咭自組水，低階又唔需要"},{"pid":"7bb6cbe4f8d8a35b129499d0200250408afc5464","tid":761764,"uid":79829,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"14e04c50e9448b2aff72e8500d0f7b65a47503c9","tid":761764,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:49:44.000Z","msg":"單排又一體水不如風冷，雙排機箱兼容性又低，出黎有幾多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚咭自組水，低階又唔需要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:37:48.000Z","msg":"顯示卡用120排效果都明顯"},